    "lines":  [
                  {
                      "line_number":  824,
                      "text":  "Since my accident my dating life has sucked",
                      "start":  2104,
                      "label":  "setup"
                  },
                  {
                      "line_number":  825,
                      "text":  "The last summer before it happened man. I was fucking killing it",
                      "start":  2108,
                      "label":  "setup"
                  },
                  {
                      "line_number":  826,
                      "text":  "I was dating one girl told me she wanted me to talk more during sex",
                      "start":  2110,
                      "label":  "setup"
                  },
                  {
                      "line_number":  827,
                      "text":  "So I did.",
                      "start":  2114,
                      "label":  "setup"
                  },
                  {
                      "line_number":  828,
                      "text":  "And then she got mad and broke up with me.",
                      "start":  2115,
                      "label":  "setup"
                  },
                  {
                      "line_number":  829,
                      "text":  "And I was like, \"I kind of think this is your fault",
                      "start":  2118,
                      "label":  "setup"
                  },
                  {
                      "line_number":  830,
                      "text":  "because when you told me you wanted me",
                      "start":  2120,
                      "label":  "setup"
                  },
                  {
                      "line_number":  831,
                      "text":  "to talk more during sex,",
                      "start":  2122,
                      "label":  "setup"
                  },
                  {
                      "line_number":  832,
                      "text":  "you should have specified that it was to you",
                      "start":  2123,
                      "label":  "setup"
                  },
                  {
                      "line_number":  833,
                      "text":  "and not on the phone.\"",
                      "start":  2125,
                      "label":  "punchline"
                  },
                  {
                      "line_number":  835,
                      "text":  "- \"But you called my dad!\"",
                      "start":  2129,
                      "label":  "tag"
                  },
                  {
                      "line_number":  836,
                      "text":  "- I\u0027m like, \"Yeah, \u0027cause we\u0027re, like, cool, you know?",
                      "start":  2131,
                      "label":  "tag"
                  },
                  {
                      "line_number":  837,
                      "text":  "And I feel like you should have known that,",
                      "start":  2134,
                      "label":  "tag"
                  },
                  {
                      "line_number":  838,
                      "text":  "especially since your dad and I graduated together.\"",
                      "start":  2135,
                      "label":  "tag"
                  },
                  {
                      "line_number":  841,
                      "text":  "Another girl I dated, she played super hard to get.",
                      "start":  2144,
                      "label":  "setup"
                  },
                  {
                      "line_number":  842,
                      "text":  "And when we finally hooked up, it was at a church.",
                      "start":  2146,
                      "label":  "setup"
                  },
                  {
                      "line_number":  843,
                      "text":  "She just laid there and kept staring at me real weird.",
                      "start":  2149,
                      "label":  "setup"
                  },
                  {
                      "line_number":  844,
                      "text":  "So I had to put coins over her eyes.",
                      "start":  2152,
                      "label":  "punchline"
                  },
                  {
                      "line_number":  845,
                      "text":  "Luckily though, she was Asian, so I only had to use pennies.",
                      "start":  2157,
                      "label":  "tag"
                  },
                  {
                      "line_number":  847,
                      "text":  "But if you can\u0027t tell, I\u0027m a Jew.",
                      "start":  2161,
                      "label":  "setup"
                  },
                  {
